      "content": "but he's really adamant that he's just dehydrated and jet lagged. he's even saying he feels a bit dizzy but that's normal after a long flight. he doesn't want to go to the hospital and make a big deal out of nothing. r u sure it's not just exhaustion? he's like 70 so he's always a bit slow to wake up in the mornings.",
